description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic, motivated and compassionate Clinical Psychologist/Cognitive Behaviour Therapist to join the adult community Eating Disorder Service which is based in Salford, Greater Manchester and holds clinics in the Greater Manchester area.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will take responsibility for providing assessments and evidence-based psychological therapies to clients in the Greater Manchester area with a range of eating disorders. Experience in this area would be desirable although not essential as training will be given.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The service prides itself on delivering high quality, evidence-based psychological and dietetic interventions and the new contracts to provide an enhanced service which are currently underway mean that this is an exciting time to join our team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameMagdalene SampsonJob titleActing Clinical LeadEmail addressmagdalene.sampson@gmmh.nhs.ukTelephone number0161 271 0508&lt;/p&gt;
